ided.}) 14. Nxd4 exd4 15. Rxd4 {We should still exercise some care to develop the remaining pieces.} Bc5 16. Rd1 Bd7 {Such small sacrifices are very common in the Catalan. White usually loses too much time taking the b7 -pawn.} 17. Bxb7 {Too greedy.} Rab8 18. Bg2 Qf5 {White can't develop the c1 -bishop as b2 is hanging.} *

