l way for White to develop, but it fails to put any real pressure on us.} O-O 10. Rc1 Rc8 {We are able to play ... c5 soon, but as White is not really intending anything soon, it makes sense to make a few preparatory moves first. For instance, kicking the bishop back with ... Nd5 makes sense, but also just making luft with ... h6 .} *

