{In the coming exercises we will review some of the ideas, plans and structures we have studied. Again, as with the tactics puzzles, we will use only positions taken from tournament practice.   In most of them, you will have to find the best game plan, but in some cases I will also ask you to evaluate an unbalanced position or an exchange.   Take your time - in these kinds of exercises you should not be in any hurry :-)} 1. Z0 *

